  "body": "### Description\nCurrently the `--ee-endpoint` option is only used if bellatrix is scheduled for the network. We should start using it if provided as the `--eth1-endpoint` even if bellatrix isn't enabled so users can prepare their mainnet setups for the merge now.\n\nWe should also ensure we accept `null` as the value for TTD in the transition configuration from the EL and consider it matching if our TTD is still the placeholder version.",
